{
  "stem": "18258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The police had already brought out the mounted force and we kept running, because when they came and eventually, the Justizpalast was set on fire.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in a side street with my mother by the way, and we finally made our way home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we got home, we-- I got into uniform, footprint uniform, and reported to our local mobilization station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I spent the next several days in uniform, occasionally on patrol duty in one of the outer districts.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that was political, non-religious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One other thing I remember about religion-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when you did not pass your exam in religion, and our rabbi was very strict.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He tried to teach us Hebrew, but he was a poor teacher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was an excellent rabbi, but he was a very poor teacher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when I again had not passed an exam, he told me he's going to flunk me for that year.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if you flunked religion, it was the only subject in school, you had to repeat the year.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Whereas any other, you were given the chance of making up after the vacation, a make up exam, and you passed on to the next grade.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In religion, it didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told him, point frank, if you flunk me, I am over 14, which was the cutoff level, I'm going down to the nearest magistrate, and I renounce my religion.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's the way I felt about religion at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He, of course, gave me a passing grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Both my brother and I, we were circumcised.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm sure all the other boys in the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My son is circumcised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know about the others.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
